<p />
<h2><a name="Introduction"> Introduction </a></h2>
<p />
<a href="http://www.disenchanted.com" target="_top">Disenchanted</a> has a <a href="http://www.disenchanted.com/dis/linkback.html" target="_top">linkback feature</a> where referral links found in their logs are published directly on the document refered to.  In fact, referral links can be constructed with paragraph numbers so that the links are injected right at a chosen spot.
<p />
<a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/ShowReferers">ShowReferers</a> [sic] is a pair of scripts inspired by this feature, for use with <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/SSI">SSI</a> and for includes in this wiki.  It does not have the paragraph link injection, but it's a start anyway.
<p />
<h2><a name="News_Status"> News &amp; Status </a></h2>
<p />
Fixed download links, added <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/PHP">PHP</a> library source
<p />
-- <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/LesOrchard">LesOrchard</a> - 19 Nov 2002
<p />
First working version.  <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/ShareAndEnjoy">ShareAndEnjoy</a>.
<p />
-- <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/LesOrchard">LesOrchard</a> - 19 Apr 2002
<p />
<h2><a name="Downloads"> Downloads </a></h2>
<p />
<ul>
<li> <a href="http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/build_referer_db_pl.txt" target="_top">http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/build_referer_db_pl.txt</a>
<ul>
<li> This script is run on a periodic basis to build a referral lookup database from access logs
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li> <a href="http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/show_referers_cgi.txt" target="_top">http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/show_referers_cgi.txt</a>
<ul>
<li> This is the CGI that does the referral lookup
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li> <a href="http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/refer_lib_php.txt" target="_top">http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/refer_lib_php.txt</a>
<ul>
<li> Display referers in <a href="/twiki/bin/view/Main/PHP">PHP</a> pages - used in <a href="http://www.decafbad.com/archive_entry.html.tmpl" target="_top">http://www.decafbad.com/archive_entry.html.tmpl</a>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li> <a href="http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/sitewide_conf_php.txt" target="_top">http://www.decafbad.com/downloads/sitewide_conf_php.txt</a>
<ul>
<li> Sample sitewide conf file used around here, needed by refer_lib.php
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
